# 🛒 E-Commerce Console Application (Java)

## 📌 Project Description
A console-based E-Commerce system developed using Core Java.
The application simulates a basic online shopping system where users can view products, add items to cart, remove products, and checkout.

## 🚀 Features
- View Products
- Add Product to Cart
- Remove Product from Cart
- Checkout System
- Bill Generation
- Cart Management

## 🛠 Concepts Used
- OOP (Classes & Objects)
- Collections Framework (ArrayList)
- Exception Handling
- Methods
- Scanner for User Input

